'''Dragon Warrior III''' (known as '''Dragon Quest III''' in Japan) is a role-playing video game for the Nintendo Entertainment System. It is the third and final game in the "Erdrick Trilogy."

==Overview==

Dragon Warrior III introduces the class system to the series, allowing players to customize their party with various job classes. The game is a prequel to Dragon Warrior I and II, revealing the origin of the legendary hero Erdrick.

